1
00:00:25,780 --> 00:00:28,180
♪Drifting aimlessly♪

2
00:00:29,180 --> 00:00:31,540
♪Not knowing where to go♪

3
00:00:31,780 --> 00:00:36,540
♪The moonlight tonight feels sorrowful♪

4
00:00:39,380 --> 00:00:42,260
♪I stand alone against it♪

5
00:00:42,780 --> 00:00:44,620
♪But I don't want to♪

6
00:00:44,980 --> 00:00:50,780
♪The longing catches me off guard♪

7
00:00:53,100 --> 00:00:58,380
♪To the silent night, I surrender myself♪

8
00:01:00,020 --> 00:01:01,500
♪Tossing and turning, lost in confusion♪

9
00:01:01,580 --> 00:01:10,620
♪In the darkness, I lose my way♪

10
00:01:28,460 --> 00:01:32,940
[Bound by Sin]

11
00:01:33,380 --> 00:01:35,980
[Episode 17]

12
00:01:36,590 --> 00:01:37,760
Yingqi sneaked back.

13
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:43,870
Have someone keep an eye on him.

14
00:01:45,200 --> 00:01:46,120
I want to see

15
00:01:46,760 --> 00:01:48,120
what the two of them are up to.

16
00:01:48,680 --> 00:01:50,400
I had someone follow him

17
00:01:50,590 --> 00:01:51,640
when I spotted him yesterday.

18
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:56,590
Still no word from Fu Cheng?

19
00:01:57,040 --> 00:01:57,590
No.

20
00:01:58,070 --> 00:01:59,760
It's chaos outside Gangcheng right now.

21
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:01,760
We've had to pull back

22
00:02:01,790 --> 00:02:02,640
from all the outside markets,

23
00:02:03,790 --> 00:02:05,920
so it's hard to keep track of things out there.

24
00:02:16,430 --> 00:02:17,630
I wonder how long

25
00:02:18,630 --> 00:02:20,280
this war will drag on.

26
00:02:28,520 --> 00:02:30,120
I've heard that Revolutionary Army

27
00:02:30,360 --> 00:02:31,870
is being organized all over the country.

28
00:02:32,400 --> 00:02:34,310
I'm not sure if Commander Chen's troops

29
00:02:34,560 --> 00:02:35,910
can handle them.

30
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:39,710
If they can,

31
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:42,150
Commander Chen will keep squeezing us

32
00:02:42,430 --> 00:02:43,430
for military funds.

33
00:02:44,280 --> 00:02:44,960
If not,

34
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:47,030
they'll just bring in a new commander

35
00:02:47,360 --> 00:02:48,280
to do the same.

36
00:02:49,800 --> 00:02:51,000
It's all the same to us.

37
00:03:49,310 --> 00:03:49,910
Yingxian?

38
00:03:51,430 --> 00:03:52,000
Yingxian!

39
00:04:07,120 --> 00:04:07,680
Yingxian.

40
00:04:08,470 --> 00:04:09,030
Yingxian!

41
00:04:09,630 --> 00:04:10,280
Yingxian!

42
00:04:10,630 --> 00:04:11,400
Yingxian!

43
00:04:15,710 --> 00:04:16,630
Yingxian!

44
00:04:16,750 --> 00:04:17,310
Yingxian!

45
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:56,270
Yingxian,

46
00:04:57,430 --> 00:04:58,240
I hope this letter

47
00:04:59,070 --> 00:04:59,950
finds you well.

48
00:05:01,270 --> 00:05:02,800
I know my sudden departure

49
00:05:03,390 --> 00:05:05,270
must have caused you confusion and worry,

50
00:05:06,360 --> 00:05:08,750
but please allow me to explain.

51
00:05:10,900 --> 00:05:12,900
[Dear Yingxian, I hope this letter finds you well. Love, Fu Cheng]

52
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:25,000
It's from Fu Cheng.

53
00:05:25,070 --> 00:05:27,000
He says he left without saying goodbye

54
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:28,160
because the army needs him.

55
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:30,630
I'm sure there's more to it than just that.

56
00:05:32,720 --> 00:05:34,190
Boss, your third eldest granduncle is here.

57
00:05:40,240 --> 00:05:41,120
Let him in.

58
00:05:48,390 --> 00:05:50,160
Granduncle, you know

59
00:05:50,310 --> 00:05:52,600
why I asked you to come over, right?

60
00:05:55,950 --> 00:05:56,800
Yingxian,

61
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:58,310
what's this about?

62
00:05:58,510 --> 00:06:00,870
Why did you call me over this early?

63
00:06:01,040 --> 00:06:02,190
Don't you know?

64
00:06:03,120 --> 00:06:03,680
What,

65
00:06:04,240 --> 00:06:05,510
didn't Yingqi talk things through with you?

66
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:06,480
How...

67
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:08,950
How did you know?

68
00:06:10,510 --> 00:06:12,070
Yingqi is my brother.

69
00:06:12,920 --> 00:06:14,360
I know

70
00:06:14,720 --> 00:06:15,830
how his mind

71
00:06:16,310 --> 00:06:17,480
works.

72
00:06:18,480 --> 00:06:20,310
I didn't make any firm promises to Yingqi.

73
00:06:20,430 --> 00:06:21,720
I'll turn him down when I get back.

74
00:06:23,360 --> 00:06:24,560
That's not what I meant, Granduncle.

75
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:26,430
I'm asking you

76
00:06:28,270 --> 00:06:29,270
to say yes.

77
00:06:32,750 --> 00:06:34,070
Don't drag me into this mess

78
00:06:34,390 --> 00:06:36,000
between you and your brother.

79
00:06:43,800 --> 00:06:45,000
My third eldest granduncle is on board.

80
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:47,270
He said he'd recommend me to be the family head

81
00:06:47,430 --> 00:06:48,830
at the end-of-year family meeting.

82
00:06:49,360 --> 00:06:51,070
As for the other granduncles,

83
00:06:51,630 --> 00:06:53,070
they didn't take a clear stand,

84
00:06:53,390 --> 00:06:54,950
but I can tell from their tone

85
00:06:55,430 --> 00:06:57,000
that they're on my side.

86
00:06:57,390 --> 00:06:58,560
Congratulations, Mr. Jiang.

87
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:04,000
Doesn't this all feel too easy?

88
00:07:05,680 --> 00:07:07,160
I almost can't believe it.

89
00:07:07,680 --> 00:07:08,750
Don't worry, Mr. Jiang.

90
00:07:09,510 --> 00:07:11,510
Whatever tricks Jiang Yingxian has up her sleeve,

91
00:07:12,070 --> 00:07:12,950
I've got a plan.

92
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:14,240
Really?

93
00:07:19,800 --> 00:07:22,950
Then here's to us getting what we want.

94
00:07:33,240 --> 00:07:33,750
Boss,

95
00:07:34,360 --> 00:07:35,950
all the uncles have replied.

96
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:37,600
They'll go along with what you suggested.

97
00:07:40,830 --> 00:07:41,480
Boss,

98
00:07:42,190 --> 00:07:44,920
won't Mr. Yingqi's tricks fail

99
00:07:45,270 --> 00:07:46,430
if we just

100
00:07:46,600 --> 00:07:47,750
bring him back?

101
00:07:48,160 --> 00:07:49,600
Why go through all this trouble

102
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:50,720
and put on a show?

103
00:07:52,950 --> 00:07:54,630
He needs to suffer a big loss first

104
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:56,000
to understand

105
00:07:56,800 --> 00:07:58,680
that nothing in this world

106
00:07:58,950 --> 00:08:00,360
can be done

107
00:08:00,360 --> 00:08:01,510
by just talking.

108
00:08:02,510 --> 00:08:05,040
Otherwise, even if I stop him this time,

109
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:07,800
he'll keep up trouble.

110
00:08:10,270 --> 00:08:11,560
Besides, I want to see

111
00:08:12,510 --> 00:08:13,920
what Fu Zhi is really up to.

112
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:16,560
Boss,

113
00:08:16,950 --> 00:08:18,390
[Jiang's Trading Company]
there's a telegram from Haicheng.

114
00:08:26,240 --> 00:08:26,750
What's wrong?

115
00:08:28,480 --> 00:08:29,430
Fu Cheng's seriously ill.

116
00:08:34,200 --> 00:08:35,150
I need to go to Haicheng.

117
00:08:36,080 --> 00:08:37,630
The family meeting is tomorrow.

118
00:08:38,320 --> 00:08:39,910
If you leave for Haicheng now,

119
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:42,030
the meeting might not go as planned.

120
00:08:51,900 --> 00:08:54,340
[Telegram]

121
00:09:12,360 --> 00:09:13,960
What's going on with Yingxian?

122
00:09:14,200 --> 00:09:15,200
How could she leave us waiting

123
00:09:15,390 --> 00:09:17,030
like this at the end-of-year family meeting?

124
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:20,390
Does she still have any respect for us?

125
00:09:21,630 --> 00:09:22,240
Maybe

126
00:09:22,750 --> 00:09:25,000
she got held up by something.

127
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:25,840
Let's wait

128
00:09:26,030 --> 00:09:26,750
a bit longer.

129
00:09:28,480 --> 00:09:29,390
Uncles,

130
00:09:30,120 --> 00:09:32,910
I'll be hosting the meeting today.

131
00:09:36,390 --> 00:09:37,200
Yingqi,

132
00:09:37,550 --> 00:09:38,960
your sister isn't here yet.

133
00:09:39,150 --> 00:09:41,120
Let's wait for her first.

134
00:09:42,960 --> 00:09:44,510
Today's meeting

135
00:09:44,840 --> 00:09:47,630
is about deciding who will be the next head of the family.

136
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:49,630
Fourth uncle,

137
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:52,320
I don't think she needs

138
00:09:53,480 --> 00:09:55,120
to be here for this.

139
00:09:58,550 --> 00:10:00,510
Besides, she left the city last night,

140
00:10:00,910 --> 00:10:02,240
so she definitely won't make it.

141
00:10:03,390 --> 00:10:04,240
Jiang Yingqi,

142
00:10:05,120 --> 00:10:07,200
even if Yingxian can't come today,

143
00:10:07,360 --> 00:10:10,120
it doesn't mean you get to take charge.

144
00:10:11,550 --> 00:10:12,120
What,

145
00:10:12,750 --> 00:10:14,240
you think you can become the family head?

146
00:10:15,120 --> 00:10:15,870
You,

147
00:10:15,870 --> 00:10:18,600
who only create problems instead of solving them,

148
00:10:19,630 --> 00:10:20,550
think you're fit for the role?

149
00:10:23,120 --> 00:10:23,870
Granduncle,

150
00:10:24,600 --> 00:10:25,480
say something.

151
00:10:29,550 --> 00:10:30,550
Yingqi,

152
00:10:31,390 --> 00:10:33,790
whether Yingxian shows up or not,

153
00:10:34,790 --> 00:10:36,550
you will not be

154
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:38,630
the head of this family.

155
00:10:42,150 --> 00:10:42,870
Granduncle,

156
00:10:43,200 --> 00:10:45,240
didn't you promise

157
00:10:45,870 --> 00:10:47,200
to support me?

158
00:10:49,440 --> 00:10:50,150
Granduncle?

159
00:10:59,440 --> 00:11:00,200
Didn't you

160
00:11:03,750 --> 00:11:05,000
all agree to let me

161
00:11:05,750 --> 00:11:07,240
become the family head?

162
00:11:09,440 --> 00:11:10,150
Why is everyone silent?

163
00:11:10,910 --> 00:11:11,750
Say something!

164
00:11:18,000 --> 00:11:19,550
Do you really think you,

165
00:11:20,150 --> 00:11:22,120
with those petty tricks of yours, are up for the role?

166
00:11:23,390 --> 00:11:24,080
Yingxian,

167
00:11:25,630 --> 00:11:26,960
didn't you leave the city last night?

168
00:11:35,480 --> 00:11:36,910
Let's get back to the previous subject.

169
00:11:38,000 --> 00:11:38,790
Uncles,

170
00:11:39,510 --> 00:11:41,870
if you agree to make Yingqi the family head,

171
00:11:42,320 --> 00:11:43,320
please raise your hands.

172
00:11:53,030 --> 00:11:54,270
See that, Yingqi?

173
00:11:55,510 --> 00:11:56,550
This is the result.

174
00:12:25,980 --> 00:12:29,780
♪If snow is winter's whispered verse♪

175
00:12:33,180 --> 00:12:37,020
♪Then tears are moles of deep remorse♪

176
00:12:40,340 --> 00:12:44,500
♪If memory speaks of you alone♪

177
00:12:46,180 --> 00:12:51,420
♪It turns to thorns that carve the stone♪

178
00:12:53,290 --> 00:12:58,700
♪Memories dance in random flight♪

179
00:12:59,220 --> 00:13:07,100
♪Beneath the stars, once you held me tight♪

180
00:13:07,380 --> 00:13:14,340
♪A thousand tears in snow did burn♪

181
00:13:14,420 --> 00:13:21,620
♪To keep you warm through winter's turn♪

182
00:13:37,620 --> 00:13:41,780
♪In the next life, a thousand partings♪

183
00:13:44,860 --> 00:13:48,500
♪Could they exchange for one new starting?♪

184
00:13:51,940 --> 00:13:56,140
♪If we could turn the clock back♪

185
00:13:57,820 --> 00:14:03,940
♪Our hearts entwined, no god could part♪

186
00:14:04,980 --> 00:14:10,300
♪Memories dance in random flight♪

187
00:14:10,820 --> 00:14:18,740
♪In winter's chill, you said "I love you" right♪

188
00:14:18,980 --> 00:14:25,900
♪A thousand snowflakes softly land♪

189
00:14:26,100 --> 00:14:32,820
♪Our trace of love can't be impaired♪

190
00:14:34,940 --> 00:14:37,900
♪The wooden bench on the street♪

191
00:14:38,540 --> 00:14:39,420
♪It recalls our first sweet meet♪
